parameters:
Even though I told you it's pointless, you came
chasing after me to get killed.
I won't silently obey, you know.

Who's saying that? You're using demonic powers
too, aren't you?
I'm not thinking about world domination.
Don't you think it's a waste?

I don't think so. This power is not meant for
humans.
That's why I'm making it my own power.

The Hero Association and the Samuel Church are
afraid.
To possess a power stronger than ourselves

But when it comes to defeating demons, we can't
afford to be picky about our methods, right?

That's true... but, we still can't handle that
power.

Actually, we're not trying to use it to defeat
demons, are we?

Well, yeah. I mean, we obtained such a strong
power.
Don't you want to try various things?

As someone who possesses Leviathan's magical
power, I understand.
Even I have done bad things while looping.

At that time, I was captivated by the magical
power.
So, I'll stop for Tommy's sake too.

After all, you're the friend who taught me so many
things at first.

It's a shame. I thought that we, who possess the
same Leviathan's magical power, might be able to
understand each other.

Don't lie. You were fully intent on defeating me,
weren't you?
If you see this power, I'm sure you'll understand.
No way... I was really summoned...

Isn't it amazing? Even without gathering magical
power through a black mass, I can summon demons.

Haa, haa... I guess I'm not in my best condition
since I was just summoned.

Ah, I didn't have much magical power, but still,
this strength...
If only we could buy more time.

But it's not a problem. If you don't have any
magical power, then just hand it over.
Hehe, I think we've worked hard enough.
Look forward to the world I create.
Why... I thought I did it properly...

Have you already recovered...? No, I've never
heard of such a recovery magic.

I haven't recovered. Besides, I haven't even been
attacked myself.

That can't be true! It's true that we captured the
vice president with a magical tool.
But, I am just a doll.

Didn't I say it before? My specialty magic is doll
manipulation magic.

I always spent my time manipulating dolls from my
room.

So, the one you were always talking about was a
doll?
But you were using magic properly too, right?

Even though the power is weakened, I can still use
magic.

I've been using doll manipulation magic since I
was little, so I can do various things.

(That planetary magic wasn't at full power... Just
how strong is she?)
I will be the one to deal with the demon.
I'll leave Tommy Martin to you guys.

Just because she's strong, doesn't mean I'll lose
so easily.
I still have stock of magical tools, you know.
Don't get cocky just because you stopped Eligor.
My true power isn't something like this.

I haven't completely taken away Leviathan's power
yet, but it's enough to fight against you guys.
I'll show you hell right now!

Why... even though I obtained the power of the
Demon King...
I can use the power of the king...!
No, Tommy can't use it at all.
You were just drowning in power.
The true magic of Leviathan is even more amazing.
What do you think you understand?!
Not yet... If only I had more magical power...
Are you still planning to do it?
I can't give you any more magical power than this.
That... is an incredible sense of intimidation...

(It's completely different from when we met in the
magic prison...)
Ah, I finally managed to get out.

The air outside the prison feels delicious after
such a long time.

Did you gather too much magical power and end up
meddling even with the magic prison management?
Masamune, you've done well to come this far.
I'm still not in top form yet.
I didn't expect you to be this strong.

Of course. I am Leviathan, one of the seven kings
of the Hell Empire, the Envy King.

As long as I don't let my guard down, there are no
enemies on the surface.

(This is not the development I expected... Did I
really make the right decision letting this person
out...)
Finally, I can achieve my goal.

It was a terrifying power. Maybe even I can't win
against it.

Leviathan... said she's not interested in
invasion.
But more importantly, what about Tommy?
It seems like Leviathan has collected everything.

I don't sense any demonic presence from Tommy-
kun.

Such... the Martin family's... long-cherished
wish...

Even if you suddenly gain excessive power, your
personality will be pulled towards the direction
of magic.

To become stronger, there's no choice but to work
hard diligently.

D-Damn it... I-I just wanted to be...
acknowledged...

(Tommy isn't so different from me. The only reason
I didn't stray from the path is because I had
Amelia.)

We will temporarily take custody of you in the
Student Council.

There are also things I want to ask about the
Student Council President.
You will be handed over to the Magic Association.
......I won't say it from my mouth.
But I don't think we can keep hiding forever.

Because our organization has captured many skilled
wizards for forbidden crimes.
(I also need to settle the score soon)

(But, there's still something I need to do before
that)
